Omnichannel strategies requiring extensive customer data raise important privacy and compliance questions. Ensure you're following GDPR, CCPA, and other relevant regulations. Be transparent with prospects about data collection and usage. Provide clear opt-in and opt-out capabilities. Build data governance practices respecting customer privacy while enabling personalization.

